INSERT INTO actorReviews (actorId, producerId, contractId, rating, review, professionalismRating, reliabilityRating, wouldHireAgain, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  c.actorId,
  c.producerId,
  c.id as contractId,
  CASE 
    WHEN u.name = 'Sarah Johnson' THEN 5
    WHEN u.name = 'Michael Chen' THEN 4
    WHEN u.name = 'Emma Rodriguez' THEN 4
    WHEN u.name = 'David Kim' THEN 5
    WHEN u.name = 'Lisa Anderson' THEN 4
  END as rating,
  CASE 
    WHEN u.name = 'Sarah Johnson' THEN 'Sarah was absolutely phenomenal! Her dedication to the role and professionalism on set made the entire production smooth. Would definitely work with her again!'
    WHEN u.name = 'Michael Chen' THEN 'Michael delivered a solid performance throughout the series. Always on time, knew his lines, and worked well with the cast.'
    WHEN u.name = 'Emma Rodriguez' THEN 'Emma brought great emotion to the role. She was professional and committed to the project.'
    WHEN u.name = 'David Kim' THEN 'David has an amazing voice and incredible range. He nailed the character perfectly!'
    WHEN u.name = 'Lisa Anderson' THEN 'Lisa brought tremendous stage presence and experience to the production. Very professional.'
  END as review,
  CASE 
    WHEN u.name = 'Sarah Johnson' THEN 5
    WHEN u.name = 'Michael Chen' THEN 5
    WHEN u.name = 'Emma Rodriguez' THEN 4
    WHEN u.name = 'David Kim' THEN 5
    WHEN u.name = 'Lisa Anderson' THEN 5
  END as professionalismRating,
  CASE 
    WHEN u.name = 'Sarah Johnson' THEN 5
    WHEN u.name = 'Michael Chen' THEN 4
    WHEN u.name = 'Emma Rodriguez' THEN 3
    WHEN u.name = 'David Kim' THEN 5
    WHEN u.name = 'Lisa Anderson' THEN 4
  END as reliabilityRating,
  true as wouldHireAgain,
  NOW() as createdAt,
  NOW() as updatedAt
FROM contracts c
JOIN users u ON c.actorId = u.id
WHERE u.openId LIKE 'sample_actor_%' AND c.status = 'completed'
